Package: chatdmdi
Type: Package
Title: Minimal ChatDMDI Launcher via ellmer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jacob", "Z", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimalist wrapper to launch an ellmer live browser chat
    against the ChatDMDI-compatible API. Starts a background process and
    opens the viewer.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
